OL,6,BFESTIVAL OF FLIGHTC     Sept 21 - Oct 5
OL,7,G                                       
OL,8,GThe first ever two-week festival of    
OL,9,Gbirds and wildlife organised by the    
OL,10,GRoyal Society for the Protection of    
OL,11,GBirds celebrates birds, wildlife and   
OL,12,Gthe environment in which they live.    
OL,13,G                                       
OL,14,GThe festival consists of more than 150 
OL,15,Gevents across the UK, culminating in   
OL,16,GWorld Birdwatch 1997.                  
OL,17,G                                       
OL,18,GFor details call the Society on        
OL,19,G01767 680551.                          
